yle=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181101173702bCQFOhgfJXYamPiL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181101173703kg4d0hlCiLmS7PEQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181101173703mI0C1c2S9o7bDMvd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181101173703J96khoKBMj482GPW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181101173703PGotSAvDkKM39Jub.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"http://www.beerslondon.com/exhibitions/andy-dixon-alchemy\" rel=\"nofollow\">加拿大艺术家 Andy Dixon 在伦敦 Beers London 画廊的展览“Alchemy”（点金术）</a></strong>。<br></p><p>今年 39 岁的 Andy Dixon 也是北温哥华市朋克乐队 d.b.s. 的成员，还成立过一个唱片厂牌&nbsp;Ache Records。他擅长用油彩探索“价值背后的心理”以及“艺术与奢侈品之间错综复杂的禁忌关系”。</p><p>此次展览中的画作使用了大量粉红色。<a href=\"https://www.itsnicethat.com/articles/andy-dixon-alchemy-art-301018\" rel=\"nofollow\">展览导言中写道</a>：“艺术与其价值之间的关系一直变幻莫测。一些看似随意的元素却会给画作的售价带来积极或消极的影响。比如颜色——那些带有红色的画作，因为在亚洲市场寓意吉祥，也会在那里卖得更好。”</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201811011806364twqEzIj6SkOcFA7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.998619\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181101180643Q7td3XNzLrcI2ZVB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.686464\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201811011806236EJZ3NIrQo7Gi4zU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.745856\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201811011806103vohxQIVSCDMA0ab.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.785912\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181101180608EHsyBgLSCcj2XTi5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.716851\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181101180615wq6jbMtNEd5Lz2kU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.656077\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181101180647od6r4gGYvQVBOHU0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.676796\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201811011806170yuMrsxv8XdLjtCH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.773481\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.itsnicethat.com/articles/caroline-tompkins-miss-america-bloomberg-businessweek-photography-301018\" rel=\"nofollow\">选美比赛在 Metoo 时代要如何自处？</a></strong></p><p>《彭博商业周刊》派摄影记者 Caroline Tompkins 带着这个问题跟踪拍摄了今年“美国小姐”选美比赛。这些影像并没有展现出特定立场或观点，相反，它们只是忠实记录了与比赛相关的疯狂和乐趣。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181101181954wUomc3Dh0XRFPEQi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181101181951c3h6kyVZD9CKARv7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181101181953pIiF6MYofVPQNlEK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181101181950FDqUCui1lWw0rBkc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.799724\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201811011819508ZfSCkLptXadBYUF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.799724\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181101181950R4WcioGmKtg3hjVz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201811011819518r3kJg5wntz0xhdC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.799724\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181101181952G9lbNMPWug0JILVD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.799724\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201811011819532NEzHrfv3QFnqMtP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181101181954AmakG9o8cqyvJgx4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.785912\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>题图为 Andy Dixon 作品</p>"}